<HEADER>
A2690 &Cx1f; ttx-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEST-TEX     12-16 0013
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEST-TEX </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Fort Worth Star-Telegram.
</P>
</TEXT>
