<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-16 14:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2845 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RAYTHEON-BURNHAM-ART-     12-16 1817
