<DOCNO> NYT19981216.0211 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-16 15:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2972 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYTBOOK-RACE-1000&AMP;ADD     12-16 1537
