<HEADLINE>
TEST YOUR LITERARY KNOWLEDGE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Thiis week's star is Jane Austen (1775-1817).
</P>
<P>
   This one's for Austen buffs, and for others who only think they
are. Match 18 characters _ three for each book _ with Jane Austen's
six novels. You pass with 10 correct answers and earn an A with 15
right. Answers are on the opposite page.
</P>
<P>
   The characters:
</P>
