   12. Fanny Price
</P>
<P>
   13. Harriet Smith
</P>
<P>
   14. John Thorpe
</P>
<P>
   15. Henry Tilney
</P>
<P>
   16. Frederick Wentworth
</P>
<P>
   17. George Wickham
</P>
