<P>
   IRAQ-IMPEACHENT (Washington) _ As President Clinton weighs
military action against Iraq, House leaders consider delaying the
floor debate on impeachment. Meanwhile, Clinton and Vice President
Al Gore appeal once more to moderate Republicans for help in their
last-ditch fight against impeachment. By STEWART M. POWELL.
</P>
