   INTERNATIONAL NEWS (``i'' category)
</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-NETANYAHU (Jerusalem) _ Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu
says he will call for early elections if the Israeli parliament
fails to give him a mandate to negotiate peace deals with the
Palestinians. By DEBORAH HORAN.
</P>
