<TEXT>
<P>
   Editors: In her op-ed, ``Protest the Impeachment Charade,'' _
slugged BC-STEINEM-ANTI-IMPEACHMENT _ Gloria Steinem writes: ``It
is time to register outraged and principled opposition to the
impeachment charade now going on in Washington.''
</P>
<P>
   Among her points:
</P>
<P>
   __ A Congress made up of nearly 90 percent men is trying to
remove the first president elected by women voters.
</P>
<P>
   __ Americans who support Clinton the MOST are those who benefit
from our economy the LEAST.
</P>
<P>
   __ Power is NOT the ultimate aphrodisiac.
</P>
<P>
   __ If Clinton is impeached, any partisan majority will be able
to impeach any president.
</P>
<P>
   __ The right wing is trying to use its version of sexual
harassment law to peacefully assassinate a president.
</P>
<P>
   ........................
