<P>
   ABUSE-DEATH (Council Grove, Kan.) _ A little boy's death puts
Kansas Department of Social and Rehabilitation Services on the
defensive. After the child was beaten in September, the mother's
boyfriend cried and signed a pledge never to do it again. That was
enough for SRS. Three weeks later, Timmie Post was dead and the
boyfriend stands accused. By Donald Bradley. Story will move in the
``a'' category.
</P>
