<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-16 17:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3406 &Cx1f; kan-z
r w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-IMPEACH-KAN &LR;      12-16 1253
