<P>
   (NYT19) JERICHO, N.Y. -- Dec. 16, 1998 -- NASD-MARKETPLACE,
12-16 -- ``The NASD is an organization that is resistant to
change,'' says Alan Davidson, president of the Independent Broker
Dealer Association and Zeus Securities, a one-office securities
firm in Jericho that specializes in bonds. Davidson is also the
force behind the independent slate of candidates for the
association's board. ``They have betrayed the bulk of their
membership.'' (Maxine Hicks/New York Times Photo) *LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT18) NEW YORK -- Dec. 16, 1998 -- NY-STEEL-DRUM, 12-16 --
Jacquii Leveine, a music major at City College, has been playing
the steel drum for nearly a decade with the encouragement of her
mother, Cynthia. The instrument is now being taught in some New
York City schools. (Linda Rosier/New York Times Photo)
</P>
