<P>
   (NYT16) NEW YORK -- Dec. 16, 1998 -- VINOLY-DESIGN, 12-16 --
Diana Vinoly decorated her son's apartment in a mix of old and new
furniture. The designer drew on the classic silhouettes of some
modern furniture designs, a testament to beauty in brevity, and
revived an old standby: the built-in wall unit. (Fred R. Conrad/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
