for U.S. and British air strikes following a report that Baghdad
had failed to cooperate fully with the arms inspectors. Any attack
by the U.S. would involve the use of Cruise Missiles, like the one
shown in this undated photo. (Boeing/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT4) LAS VEGAS -- Dec. 16, 1998 -- CIR-GAMBLE-2, 12-16 -- A
